show.description: A cleaner, Aaryan, saves a rich girl, Avni, from the clutches of a wealthy man. Aaryan is actually a secret head of the syndicate and is called Ghost, but he has hidden this identity from everyone – even his own son. How will he navigate his life while also fighting his enemies on his journey? Watch now!
